{
  "3058710": {
    "name": "JumpMap",
    "steam_appid": 3058710,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058710/extras/8763aa38121745c9e81928c141efbab6.avif?t=1762535304\" width=600 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>JumpMap </strong>是一款激动人心的第一人称3D平台游戏，具有一个特殊的机制：每次你掉落时，你会回到之前所在的位置。探索20多个精心设计的关卡，挑战你的精确度和时机技巧。现在还有速度跑模式：穿越所有关卡并记录你最好的时间！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你唯一的目标是到达每个关卡的顶部。专注于攀爬、通过挑战，磨练你的能力以征服每一个上升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058710/extras/80307cfa19951fbda0ec32a8f279c04b.poster.avif?t=1762535304\" width=600 height=271 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058710/extras/80307cfa19951fbda0ec32a8f279c04b.webm?t=1762535304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>速度跑模式</strong>：一次性通关所有关卡，时钟倒计时。记录你的时间并争取最佳成绩。与自己和朋友竞速，争夺最快通关时间！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>最佳时间跟踪</strong>：通过测量完成每个关卡的速度来跟踪你的进度，并查看你的个人最佳时间，增加挑战和提高。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>双重跳跃</strong>：掌握空中再次跳跃的能力，完美你的技巧，征服最棘手的平台，达到新的高度。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>手柄和Steam Deck支持</strong>：无论你使用手柄还是在Steam Deck上游玩，都能享受流畅的游戏体验，让你随时随地畅玩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>纯平台玩法</strong>：专注于你的平台技巧，没有干扰——没有BOSS、武器或NPC——只有你和征服每次攀登与跳跃的乐趣。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超低图形选项</strong>：通过专为老旧计算机设计的复古图形设置优化你的游戏体验，确保顺畅的游戏过程而不妥协于乐趣。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自动回退</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你掉落了，不需要重新开始关卡；自动回退功能会在每个平台上保存你的进度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058710/extras/823596401bb30feb0f72ff05c9236d6a.poster.avif?t=1762535304\" width=600 height=259 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058710/extras/823596401bb30feb0f72ff05c9236d6a.webm?t=1762535304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>速度跑模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战自己，在时钟计时下完成所有关卡的一次性通关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058710/extras/877a2e3e822d827be2a91fa03a279fdb.avif?t=1762535304\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>最佳时间</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与时钟竞赛，挑战自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058710/extras/d5fa9da0660d15a36b15c65f26f1b073.avif?t=1762535304\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>20+ 关卡</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的每个关卡都经过精心制作，确保每个平台都经过深思熟虑的设计，并战略性地放置，以为玩家提供具有挑战性和奖励性的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058710/extras/a5e8f613e4c11be76393d325be854888.poster.avif?t=1762535304\" width=600 height=405 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058710/extras/a5e8f613e4c11be76393d325be854888.webm?t=1762535304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>低压力环境</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏中你找不到的东西：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >惊吓</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生命值条</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>JumpMap是由一名独立开发者制作的爱心作品，所有关卡均为手工制作。</i></p>",
